# Public, browser-safe identifier only - never a secret. Astro exposes
# PUBLIC_-prefixed variables to client-side code (see astro.config.mjs).
#
# Unset by default. Leaving this empty keeps all tracking safely inactive -
# see src/lib/tracking/README.md for the full activation checklist.
#
# Format: GTM-XXXXXXX (this example value is a placeholder, not a real id).
PUBLIC_GTM_CONTAINER_ID=
